data.description: MUST SEE !  This home is a must see in a convenient Dover location.  This home has beautiful woodwork throughout.   Spacious kitchen with plenty of cupboard space with a large pantry area.  Four bedrooms with oversized closets and one full bath.  Possible fifth bedroom or office space.  Walk up attic for extra storage space.  This home sits on a sizable corner lot.  2 stall garage with a new belt driven garage door opener installed.  Outdoor storage shed with electricity.   New glass block windows installed in basement.   This home is conveniently located close to schools, shopping, restaurants and I-77.  Call today for a private showing.
